-+--+Custom Domains
-+--+kingdomsofaether.com
-+--+Effort: 4x
-+--+
-+--+Custom Domains + Creator Subdomains
-+--+wiki.kingdomsofaether.com
-+--+community.kingdomsofaether.com
-+--+Effort: 8x
-+--+
-+--+Important Observation
-+--+
-+--+Players care far more about:
-+--+      Rewards
-+--+      Content
-+--+      Events
-+--+      Challenges
-+--+
-+--+Than URL structure.
-+--+Most players will happily visit:
-+--+gamefoundrystudio.com/kingdoms-of-aether/challenges/dragon-of-
-+--+the-day
-+--+if they receive:
-+--+100 Gems
-+--+Therefore:
-+--+Build ecosystem features first.
-+--+Build URL sophistication later.
-+--+
-+--+Recommended Rollout Plan
-+--+
-+--+V1 - Path URLs
-+--+
-+--+Primary format:
-+--+gamefoundrystudio.com/kingdoms-of-aether
-+--+Simple.
-+--+Fast.
-+--+Lowest effort.
-+--+Highest value.
-+--+
-+--+V2 - Wildcard Subdomains
-+--+
-+--+Examples:
-+--+kingdoms-of-aether.gamefoundrystudio.com
-+--+wiki.kingdoms-of-aether.gamefoundrystudio.com
-+--+news.kingdoms-of-aether.gamefoundrystudio.com
-+--+Premium feel.
-+--+Still fully controlled by GFS.
-+--+
-+--+V3 - Bring Your Own Domain
-+--+
-+--+Examples:
-+--+kingdomsofaether.com
-+--+playkingdomsofaether.com
-+--+Creator purchases domain elsewhere.
-+--+GFS hosts and manages routing.
-+--+
-+--+V4 - Creator Domain Subdomains
-+--+
-+--+Examples:
-+--+wiki.kingdomsofaether.com
-+--+community.kingdomsofaether.com
-+--+news.kingdomsofaether.com
-+--+Highest effort.
-+--+Lowest initial priority.
-+--+
-+--+DNS Architecture
-+--+
-+--+Never point creators directly at an IP address.
-+--+Always point creators at a hostname controlled by GFS.
-+--+Example:
-+--+www.kingdomsofaether.com
-+--+CNAME domains.gamefoundrystudio.com
-+--+Flow:
-+--+Creator Domain
-+--+↓
-+--+CNAME
-+--+↓
-+--+domains.gamefoundrystudio.com
-+--+↓
-+--+Cloudflare
-+--+↓
-+--+Game Foundry Studio
-+--+Benefits:
-+--+
-+--+      Infrastructure changes are invisible to creators
-+--+      No DNS updates required when hosting changes
-+--+      Cloudflare remains in front of all traffic
-+--+      Simplifies scaling and migration
-+--+This should be considered the preferred architecture for all future
-+--+custom-domain support.
-+--+
-+--+Long-Term Strategic Goal
-+--+
-+--+The strategic asset is not the engine.
-+--+               The strategic asset is:
-+--+               Thousands of game ecosystems living under one roof.
-+--+               Future players should say:
-+--+               "I found this game on Game Foundry Studio."
-+--+               not:
-+--+               "I found this random website somewhere."
-+--+               That network effect is what transforms GFS from a game creation
-+--+               tool into a game platform.
-+--+
-+--+This is one of the strongest platform-level ideas we've discussed because it directly ties
-+--+together Game Journey → Community → Discovery → Marketplace → Retention →
-+--+Monetization into a single ecosystem instead of treating them as separate features.
